data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT! This Split Level home is located on a large corner lot in,  Open kitchen with black appliances.  From your kitchen walk onto the large deck overlooking the large fenced back yard.. Good for grilling or just relaxing. The  Dinning area is off of the Kitchen shared with the Living Room area.  All 3 bedrooms  and 1 full Bath are on the upper level. Lower level Family Room with 2 flex rooms that can be used as an Office, Fitness, Guest Room or whatever you like and 1 full Bath. The wood stove and 2 sheds in the backyard conveys. Great location! near local shopping, restaurants, BWI Airport, local parks and much more. Seller is offering $2000 concessions at asking price.
